{"tid":1331611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毒果頭版篤灰：回應香港示威者到台尋庇護報道　蔡英文稱基於人道處理","createTime":"2019-07-19T04:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T04:16:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13839aa7b562b341c89813d2de69b406b8fee21f","tid":1331611,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1469185_1_L_20190719103445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1469185_1_L_20190719103445.jpg&h=11f8aead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469185-20190719.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469185-20190719.htm&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=f87bcd3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469185-20190719.htm&h=fbf2aad5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469185-20190719.htm</a><br />\n正在加勒比海友邦訪問的台灣蔡英文總統，回應有報道指，有香港反修訂逃犯條例的示威者，到台灣尋求庇護。她說，相信有關單位掌握情況，對於這些來自香港的朋友，會基於人道適當處理。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會昨日未有證實是否曾經與示威者接觸，但就說如果政府收到申請，會在尊重人權的原則下，由相關單位依法妥善處理。"},{"pid":"6a5128c33ea5ca5daf0f18ba58208241c20ffcb7","tid":1331611,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T04:16:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主分化撚，blocked 上一頁</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【杜絕分化】熱狗惡行 24小時輪流廣播 （2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}